name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb

reviews.name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb
reviews.reviewText: I FOUND A BUG-ZAPPER IN A SECOND A STORE BACK IN THE EARLY 80s. PAID $10 FOR IT & LASTED UNTILL 2005. NOW!! I GOT THIS ONE BACK IN 2009, LASTED ALMOST 3 MNTHS. EXCHANGED IT & 2nd ONE LASTED INTO 2010, ABOUT 5 MNTHS. THE NEXT YEAR ( 2011 ) IN THE SPRING WENT BACK TO WALMART & AGAIN, THIS MODEL IS ALL THEY HAD. SOOO, I GOT IT, & IT LASTED AROUND 6 MNTHS. HERE I AM, SPRING OF 2012 LOOKING FOR MY 4th ZAPPER & AGAIN, THIS IS ALL THEY HAVE. I'M GOING TO LOOK ELSEWHERE, I MISS THE GOOD 'OL AMERICAN MADE QUALITY DAYS !!
reviews.title: DONT WAIST YOUR MONEY !!

reviews.name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb
reviews.reviewText: Excellent product for the money, we bought it for all the mosquitoes since we have woods behind our house. Since we've been using it almost every day the mosquito problem is down 99% and love every minute of the freedom from bites.
reviews.title: Excellent product

reviews.name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb
reviews.reviewText: Its had been years since we had updated and this just dont compare to the old models but I m guessing it safer the the old ones.. It does work and the dusk til dawn is nice. But just dont have the zapp! Looking at the feedback on the other models I cant amagine what the other ones are like,if this is the best. :(
reviews.title: Not much compared to the old model we had.......

reviews.name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb
reviews.reviewText: it does everything that it said
reviews.title: 25 April 2012

reviews.name: Black Flag 40W Deluxe Bug Zapper with Black Bulb
reviews.reviewText: The unit works good so far as killing bugs, HOWEVER, it cloggs up with bugs and you have to blow them out before it can continue to kill more bugs. I bought this brand and a Flowtron BK-40D and it is SO much better because it NEVER gets clogged up with bugs. Get a Flowtron for sure!!
reviews.title: It's ok, just clogs up with bugs
